s a new context before rendering its subtree, isolating child preferences"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Collect"}]},{"type":"text","text":": After the subtree finishes, the modifier pops the context (merging into the parent) and fires the callback with the scoped result"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Discard"}]},{"type":"text","text":": At the start of the next frame, everything resets: stale preferences never persist"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This per-frame reset ensures preferences always reflect the current view tree. Removed views stop contributing automatically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Reduce-Strategies","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Reduce Strategies"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reduce"},{"type":"text","text":" function determines how multiple children’s values combine. Common patterns:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Strategy","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implementation","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Last value wins"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"value = nextValue()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (default)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Titles, labels: deepest child wins","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Additive"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value += nextValue()"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Counting items, summing heights","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array coll